LITB117.title: Beaver's Team
LITB117.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 117 Beaver's Team.m4v
LITB117.description: When Wally and Eddie coach Beaver's summer football team and give them a secret play to use against the opposing team, Beaver finds out that the best way to keep a secret is to not tell it...to anyone!

LISP35.title: The Prisoners of Space
LISP35.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 35 - The Prisoners Of Space.m4v
LISP35.description: The Robinsons are tried for space crimes and the evidence shows that Smith is really responsible for the mishaps.

LITB118.title: Beaver Won't Eat
LITB118.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 118 Beaver Won't Eat.m4v
LITB118.description: When Beaver refuses to eat his Brussels sprouts, Ward and June try to find a compromise in their differing opinions on discipline, with surprising results.

LITB119.title: Beaver's House Guest
LITB119.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 119 Beaver's House Guest.m4v
LITB119.description: Ward and June are concerned when they discover that Beaver's visiting friend Chopper has divorced parents but soon see that Chopper's own experience will serve as Beaver's best lesson on this life changing event.

SPRA48.title: Junk Car Grand Prix
SPRA48.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 48 Junk Car Grand Prix.mp4
SPRA48.description: The Junkyard Grand Prix is hosted by a rich baron in honour of his missing daughter. But in fact she appears in the race as an unknowing competitor to Speed.

LISP34.title: Space Circus
LISP34.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 34 - Space Circus.m4v
LISP34.description: A space circus comes to town and the owner wants Will to run away with it.

SOKO24.title: Hydrazona, a Terrifying Bacteria
SOKO24.description: Hydrazone Bacteria; a liquid monster with acidic body and an ability to move over water wreaks havoc, dissolving anything it wants, even metal and people. Will Johnny and Giant Robot overcome this terrific Bacteria and massive Ice ally.

LITB120.title: Beaver Becomes a Hero
LITB120.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 120 Beaver Becomes a Hero.m4v
LITB120.description: Beaver's slightly exaggerated story about rescuing an abandoned canoe while fishing with Wally takes on a life of its own while passing through the school grapevine and Beaver finds that not being completely truthful can have disastrous results.

LISP36.title: The Android Machine
LISP36.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 36 - The Android Machine.m4v
LISP36.description: Doctor Smith creates an android that they teach to be more human. A humanoid shows up looking for payment for the android.

HOLM02.title: The Dancing Men
HOLM02.description: A gentleman is baffled when the childish drawings of little dancing men terrify his American wife. Sherlock Holmes soon discovers why.

SPRA47.title: Car with a Brain
SPRA47.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 47 Car with a Brain.mp4
SPRA47.description: A mad scientist brings to life a monster car that wreaks mayhem and destruction across the country. Can Speed stop it?

LITB116.title: The Last Day of School
LITB116.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 116 The Last Day of School.m4v
LITB116.description: Over breakfast on the last day of school before summer vacation, Beaver and Wally sneak a peek at the gift June bought for Beaver to give to his teacher. The embarrassed boys find a lacy slip and, not knowing that the department store made a mistake and that his gift was supposed to be handkerchiefs, Beaver must decide whether to give Miss Landers the slip or nothing at all.

LISP33.title: Forbidden World
LISP33.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost In Space 33 - Forbidden World.m4v
LISP33.description: The Robinsons encounter a hermit who plans to attack the Jupiter 2 with his army.

MDGT1936.title: Mr. Deeds Goes to Town
MDGT1936.description: A unassuming greeting card poet from a small town in Vermont heads to New York City upon inheriting a massive fortune and is immediately hounded by those who wish to take advantage of him. Stars Gary Cooper.
